Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.35,0:00:21.20,Dialogue,Manabu,0,0,0,,În ultimii doi ani, am fost foarte mândru și recunoscător
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.20,0:00:24.46,Dialogue,Manabu,0,0,0,,să conduc colectivul elevilor în postura de președinte al consiliului elevilor.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.18,0:00:29.72,Dialogue,Manabu,0,0,0,,Deși este simplist, \Ndiscursul meu se încheie aici.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.17,0:00:33.22,Dialogue,Manabu,0,0,0,,Vă mulțumesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.23,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Înainte, Horikita ar fi fost \Nimposibil de consolat.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.87,0:00:41.87,Dialogue,MC,0,0,0,,Îți mulțumim pentru toată munca depusă, președinte Horikita.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.90,0:00:47.22,Dialogue,MC,0,0,0,,Acum, vom asculta câteva cuvinte de la noul președinte al consiliului elevilor.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:50.91,0:00:54.25,Dialogue,Nagumo,0,0,0,,Eu sunt noul vostru președinte \Nal consiliului elevilor,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.25,0:00:57.74,Dialogue,Nagumo,0,0,0,,Nagumo Miyabi din clasa 2-A.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.15,0:00:59.65,Dialogue,Nagumo,0,0,0,,Voi trece direct la subiect:
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.65,0:01:05.25,Dialogue,Nagumo,0,0,0,,Vreau să transform această școală într-o meritocrație.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.65,0:01:08.36,Dialogue,Nagumo,0,0,0,,Elevii capabili se vor afla în vârf,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.36,0:01:10.71,Dialogue,Nagumo,0,0,0,,pe când ceilalți vor fi la urmă.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:10.71,0:01:12.90,Dialogue,Nagumo,0,0,0,,Așa ar trebui să fie lucrurile.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.30,0:01:22.68,Dialogue,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,Prestația ta de la festivalul \Nsportiv chiar m-a impresionat.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:23.06,0:01:24.29,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.29,0:01:28.81,Dialogue,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,Te rog s-o avertizezi pe \NHorikita să aibă grijă la Ryuen.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.11,0:01:33.32,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Nu ai colaborat cu el în trecut?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.89,Dialogue,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,Spre rușinea mea, da.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.89,0:01:38.45,Dialogue,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,Nu ar fi trebuit niciodată \Nsă am de a face cu el.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.37,0:01:42.20,Dialogue,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,Ryuen e inamicul nostru comun.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.49,0:01:43.78,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Am înțeles.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:43.78,0:01:45.33,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,O voi avertiza.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.33,0:01:46.44,Dialogue,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,Mersi.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.81,0:01:53.37,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Se pare că ambele părți își \Nfac griji în legătură cu el.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.37,0:01:54.33,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Hei...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.26,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Ei bine...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.26,0:02:00.45,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Ai câteva minute?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.45,0:02:02.42,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Vreau să te întreb ceva.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.08,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Asta ar putea suna puțin ciudat...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.58,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Dar...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.24,0:03:45.24,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Te vezi cu cineva în acest moment?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.44,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Ei bine...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.49,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Ce vrei să spui prin asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.49,0:03:50.90,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,La ce crezi că mă refer?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.90,0:03:53.15,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Te întreb dacă ai prietenă!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.48,0:03:54.83,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Deci?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.46,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Nu.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.86,0:04:00.59,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Oh... serios?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.62,0:04:04.95,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Putem avea o relație platonică și toate cele...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.45,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Deci mi-ar plăcea să facem schimb de numerele de telefon.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.07,0:04:11.72,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Bănuiesc că e în regulă.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.79,0:04:17.15,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Dar de ce eu?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.15,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Cursa de la festivalul sportiv.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.29,0:04:24.91,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Ai fost incredibil acolo...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.33,0:04:30.98,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Nu mi-am dat seama niciodată de cât de grozav... matur și drăguț ești...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.78,0:04:37.13,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,O-Oricum, asta e tot ce voiam!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.93,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Văd destul de multe fețe serioase...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.26,0:04:51.43,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Vă voi arăta acum rezultatele la testele de la jumătatea semestrului.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.53,0:04:54.94,Dialogue,Student,0,0,0,,Pe bune?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.49,Dialogue,Yamauchi,0,0,0,,Vai, a fost cât pe ce!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.49,0:05:01.07,Dialogue,Ike,0,0,0,,Hei! Priviți punctajul lui Ken!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.59,0:05:05.91,Dialogue,Sudo,0,0,0,,Grozav!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.91,0:05:07.85,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Nu e un rezultat pentru \Ncare să faci atâta zarvă.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.61,0:05:10.33,Dialogue,Sudo,0,0,0,,D-Da...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.94,0:05:12.78,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Parcă ar fi cățelușul ei.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.78,0:05:16.08,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,După cum puteți vedea, nimeni nu va fi exmatriculat de această dată.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.47,0:05:18.92,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,În cei trei ani de când îndrum clasa D,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:18.92,0:05:23.84,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,nu am avut nicio perioadă atât de lungă fără ca nicio persoană să nu fie nevoită să renunțe.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.09,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,V-ați descurcat bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:26.46,0:05:29.40,Dialogue,Miyake,0,0,0,,E asta prima oară când a \Nspus ceva bun despre noi?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:26.81,0:05:29.92,Dialogue,Ike,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bănuiesc că merităm să fim \Nlăudați din când în când!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.02,Dialogue,Yamauchi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Da!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.09,0:05:32.60,Dialogue,Yukimura,0,0,0,,Totuși, parcă ne laudă doar \Nde dragul de a o face...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.60,0:05:36.10,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Dar e prea devreme să răsuflați ușurați.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.45,0:05:38.96,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Va trebui să dați tot ce puteți la următorul examen special,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.96,0:05:40.98,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,care va servi drept \Nexamenul vostru final.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.41,0:05:44.36,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Cunoscut ca Amestecarea Lucrărilor.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.38,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Amestecarea Lucrărilor?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.38,0:05:51.81,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,La acest examen, toți elevii vor participa în grupuri de două persoane.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.74,Dialogue,Hasabe,0,0,0,,Adică în perechi, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.74,0:05:56.51,Dialogue,Ike,0,0,0,,Eu vreau să fiu în echipă cu Kikyo!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.11,0:05:59.19,Dialogue,Sakura,0,0,0,,În echipe de câte doi...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.14,0:06:04.86,Dialogue,Shinohara,0,0,0,,Karuizawa, tu vei fi cu Hirata, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.86,0:06:05.94,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,C-Ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.94,0:06:08.38,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Dar... ne putem alege noi echipele?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.38,0:06:12.39,Dialogue,Sato,0,0,0,,Cum sunt alese echipele, mai exact?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.02,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Nu te grăbi așa.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.87,0:06:21.06,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Modul de formare al echipelor va fi anunțat după micuțul test de săptămâna viitoare.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.77,Dialogue,Yamauchi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alt{\i0} test?!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.77,0:06:28.92,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Scopul lui va fi de a vă determina nivelul academic, curent.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:29.27,0:06:32.34,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Nu veți fi penalizați pentru punctaje mici, \Nnici măcar dacă luați zero puncte.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.19,0:06:35.15,Dialogue,Matsushita,0,0,0,,Ce ușurare!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.15,0:06:41.04,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Dar rezultatul la acel test va fi crucial pentru Amestecarea Lucrărilor.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.80,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Dacă, la următorul examen special,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.80,0:06:50.31,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,punctajul total al echipei \Neste sub șaizeci de puncte,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.31,0:06:52.55,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,ambii elevi vor fi exmatriculați.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.46,0:06:55.64,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Spre exemplu, dacă Ike și \NHirata sunt în aceeași echipă,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.32,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,iar Ike ia 0 puncte, cât timp Hirata ia peste 60 de puncte,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.32,0:06:59.44,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,niciunul nu va fi exmatriculat.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.44,0:07:03.81,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Există, de asemenea, un punctaj minim ce trebuie obținut adunând rezultatele la toate materiile.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.21,0:07:06.86,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Vă voi da numărul exact mai târziu,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:06.86,0:07:11.20,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,dar, în general, e în jur de 700 de puncte la toate cele opt materii.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.20,0:07:18.33,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ceea ce înseamnă că fiecare trebuie să ia în jur de 44 de puncte pe materie.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.93,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Încă un lucru.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:19.93,0:07:24.08,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Întrebările de la lucrări vor fi făcute de voi.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.34,Dialogue,Sudo,0,0,0,,Ce?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.75,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Iar la întrebările făcute de fiecare clasă,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.75,0:07:31.15,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,va răspunde una dintre celelalte trei clase.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.49,0:07:36.60,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Puteți, de asemenea, să alegeți ce clasă sperați să vă primească întrebările.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.99,0:07:39.73,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,În cazul în care două clase vor cere aceeași clasă, se va trage la sorți.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.14,0:07:44.71,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Și clasa care va lua mai multe \Npuncte dintre cele două,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.71,0:07:49.24,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,va fura 50 de puncte clasă de la cealaltă.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.11,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Ca un atac direct.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.11,0:07:55.87,Dialogue,Yukimura,0,0,0,,Dar dacă vor exista întrebări \Nla care nu există răspuns?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.86,0:07:59.37,Dialogue,Koenji,0,0,0,,Mi-ar plăcea să văd asemenea întrebări!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.37,0:08:01.11,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Nu aveți de ce să vă faceți griji.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.45,0:08:02.77,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Ceilalți profesori și cu mine
Dialogue: 100,0:08:02.77,0:08:05.40,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,vom verifica întrebările ca să ne asigurăm că asta nu se va întâmpla.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.94,0:08:08.99,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Evident, dacă trișați veți fi picați imediat
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.99,0:08:11.38,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,și apoi, ambii membri exmatriculați.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.01,0:08:18.64,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,La Amestecarea Lucrărilor, una sau două echipe sunt exmatriculate în fiecare an.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.19,0:08:20.89,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Țineți minte asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.99,0:08:27.70,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Vă voi trimite un e-mail cu regulile în detaliu în privința alcătuirii întrebărilor.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.88,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,Voi lăsa restul în seama voastră.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.78,0:08:34.28,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Ce părere ai de următorul examen?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.75,0:08:36.91,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Știu cum să câștigăm.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.53,0:08:40.57,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Explicația profesoarei noastre ne-a dat toate indiciile de care avem nevoie.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.57,0:08:41.54,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Serios?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.41,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Cheamă-i pe Hirata și ceilalți.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.37,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Vreau să ținem o întâlnire strategică.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.37,0:08:46.61,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Am înțeles.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.80,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vreau să te întreb ceva.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.55,0:08:56.66,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sato ți-a cerut să fiți împreună, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.83,0:09:03.81,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cine ți-a dat această informație?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.81,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Sato mi-a spus, evident!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.13,0:09:13.82,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Câteva fete, printre care și eu, știam că-ți va cere să fiți împreună.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.45,0:09:19.90,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Ei bine, nu e ca și cum știe cum funcționează lumea fetelor.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.09,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,M-a văzut?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.09,0:09:29.38,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Darn it! Sometimes he's so dense, \Nand sometimes he's so sharp!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.33,Dialogue,Hirata,0,0,0,,Karuizawa-san!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.47,0:09:35.04,Dialogue,Hirata,0,0,0,,Horikita-san wanted to \Ndiscuss the upcoming exam.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.04,0:09:37.56,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,S-Sure! Got it.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.77,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,I'd like to begin the \Nstrategy meeting promptly.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.36,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,What, here?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.36,0:09:46.06,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Big no to that!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.35,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Why not a café or something?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.15,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Right, Yosuke... kun?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.85,0:09:53.00,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.28,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Pallet, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.25,Dialogue,Kushida,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.27,0:09:58.28,Dialogue,Kushida,0,0,0,,Do you think I could join in?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.15,0:10:02.62,Dialogue,Kushida,0,0,0,,Or would you rather I not?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.31,Dialogue,Hirata,0,0,0,,I'd love to have you!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.31,0:10:07.17,Dialogue,Hirata,0,0,0,,You know so much about what's \Ngoing on in the class.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.81,0:10:10.79,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Of course, Kushida-san.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.79,0:10:14.54,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,I'd planned on talking to you \Nsooner or later regardless.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.54,0:10:15.72,Dialogue,Kushida,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.21,0:10:19.51,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Could the rest of you go on ahead?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.46,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,We need to fetch my bag first.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.11,Dialogue,Sudo,0,0,0,,We'll save you a seat!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:29.34,0:10:32.27,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Is it all right to let \NKushida in on our planning?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.68,0:10:35.15,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,It would look suspicious if I \Nturned her down in that context.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:36.14,0:10:40.58,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,And I'm sure there's a reason \Nyou sent them on ahead.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.13,0:10:43.83,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,I don't care for airing a \Nperson's dirty laundry...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.22,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,But I feel I should tell you...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.63,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,about Kushida-san's past.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.43,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Kushida-san and I...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:08.09,0:11:10.19,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,We attended the same middle school.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:12.22,0:11:16.90,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,The school was well attended, \Nand we were never in the same class,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:17.25,0:11:19.38,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,so it took me some time to remember her.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:20.71,0:11:23.62,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,One day, as our middle school \Ngraduation drew near,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:26.13,0:11:27.81,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,an incident occurred
Dialogue: 100,0:11:28.78,0:11:31.18,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,that tore one of the classes apart.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:33.14,0:11:35.50,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,And the rumor spread...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:36.70,0:11:38.43,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,that the one who started it all
Dialogue: 100,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.19,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,was a single female student.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:44.58,0:11:46.19,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,And you believe it was Kushida?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:46.91,0:11:49.01,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,It's all rumors, of course.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.80,0:11:52.70,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,I don't know exactly what happened,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:53.11,0:11:57.18,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,but the class remained in \Nturmoil until graduation.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:58.33,0:12:02.49,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,But how could a single person \Ndestroy an entire class?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:03.56,0:12:05.62,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,I can think of a few ways.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:06.86,0:12:08.33,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Listen, Horikita...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:09.02,0:12:12.22,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Do you know what the strongest \Nweapon in this world is?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:13.63,0:12:14.98,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:15.70,0:12:18.09,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Violence, I suppose.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.83,0:12:22.95,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Nobody can stop violence \Noccurring in front of their eyes.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.95,0:12:25.02,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,That's not Kushida's style.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:25.95,0:12:30.91,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,If Kushida wields a power of \Nequal potency to violence...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.35,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,One way or another,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:33.82,0:12:35.99,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Kushida-san sees me as an obstacle.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:36.35,0:12:39.61,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Even though I have no idea \Nwhat even happened...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.62,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,I'm sure she doesn't believe that's true.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:43.69,0:12:47.62,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Direct action might be preferable \Nover trying to convince her.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:50.53,0:12:53.09,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Get Kushida-san expelled, you mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:53.09,0:12:56.71,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,A strong offense is frequently \Nthe most effective defense.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:57.61,0:13:02.76,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,You're the one who admonished me for \Nconsidering cutting Sudo-kun loose.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:03.66,0:13:07.94,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Kushida will continue to plague \Nus until you're expelled.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:09.39,0:13:14.02,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Things have only gotten this bad, in part, \Nbecause I've refused to confront her.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.52,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,And Kushida-san is quite talented.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.94,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,She could be a considerable asset to Class D.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.89,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,You think you can bring her to our side?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:23.89,0:13:24.84,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:24.84,0:13:27.13,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,I'm going to keep talking to her.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:27.13,0:13:30.66,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,And I {\i1}will{\i0} make her understand.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:32.55,0:13:33.67,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:34.09,0:13:37.67,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,If you're that determined, \NI'll watch from afar.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:38.59,0:13:40.52,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,"Watch from afar"?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:41.03,0:13:42.69,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,But I'll ask you to refrain from
Dialogue: 100,0:13:42.69,0:13:45.30,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,protecting me the way you \Ndid at the sports festival.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.98,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,You knew about that?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:46.98,0:13:48.62,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,I had an idea.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:48.98,0:13:53.03,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,I was annoyed that you took action \Non the assumption that I'd fail,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:53.58,0:13:57.36,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,but I won't argue, \Ngiven how things turned out.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:57.36,0:13:59.06,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.39,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:02.98,0:14:05.56,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,If not for you, right now, I'd...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:07.34,0:14:08.29,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:15.01,0:14:17.70,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,An extremely roundabout \Nexpression of gratitude.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:20.37,0:14:26.21,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,Seems to me there's been too much \Nthat's off in these recent exams.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:27.53,0:14:30.20,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,Too much to be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:30.68,0:14:34.56,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,The mastermind pulling Class D's strings...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:34.93,0:14:37.59,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,And the spy helping them out...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:38.70,0:14:41.06,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,I know it's one of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:41.06,0:14:43.58,Dialogue,Ibuki,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.52,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,All right, you lot.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:46.52,0:14:49.98,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,Do you know what the strongest \Npower in this world is?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:51.15,0:14:54.59,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,It's unrestrained violence.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.62,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,I'll give you one last chance.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:57.62,0:15:01.69,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,Come clean, and I'll let your betrayal slide.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:02.58,0:15:05.83,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,Do exactly as I say, and I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:05.83,0:15:08.57,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,But if you play dumb with me...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.04,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:19.04,0:15:21.10,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,Can't even look me in the eye,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:22.09,0:15:23.22,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,Manabe?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:25.37,0:15:28.36,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,You're the traitor, aren't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.98,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,You think I didn't know the whole time?!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:34.98,0:15:38.45,Dialogue,Manabe,0,0,0,,I... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:39.42,0:15:42.48,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it. I forgive you.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:42.48,0:15:44.30,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,Just tell me one thing...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:45.35,0:15:49.46,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,Who's the mastermind behind it all?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.16,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.16,0:15:57.97,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,Bullying can be a very amusing pastime.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.59,Dialogue,Ibuki,0,0,0,,How stupid can you get?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:59.59,0:16:02.48,Dialogue,Ibuki,0,0,0,,Just for that, you sold us \Nout to their ringleader?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.87,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,Go easy on them, Ibuki.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:05.87,0:16:08.55,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,I've already said I forgive them.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:09.38,0:16:13.49,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,And you claim Yukimura and Ayanokoji \Nwere the only witnesses?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:15.03,0:16:18.37,Dialogue,Kaneda,0,0,0,,In other words, the mastermind \Nis one of those two?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.04,Dialogue,Ibuki,0,0,0,,Hang on a minute.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:20.04,0:16:22.21,Dialogue,Ibuki,0,0,0,,I've had a few interactions with Ayanokoji,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:22.21,0:16:24.25,Dialogue,Ibuki,0,0,0,,and he didn't seem like \Nthat kind of person to me!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:24.25,0:16:26.26,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,Ayanokoji...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:31.34,0:16:36.02,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,It seems almost too obvious \Nto be plausible...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:37.16,0:16:39.11,Dialogue,Ryuen,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll use {\i1}her{\i0}.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:52.17,0:16:54.39,Dialogue,Kushida,0,0,0,,Hey, over here!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:54.39,0:16:56.66,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Hey, took you long enough!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.16,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,What've you been up to?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:58.16,0:16:59.82,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,We'll start at once.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:59.82,0:17:01.41,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Total brush-off, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.29,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Typical, I guess...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:03.71,0:17:06.19,Dialogue,Kushida,0,0,0,,We're talking about Paper Shuffle, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:06.19,0:17:07.06,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:07.06,0:17:10.92,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,The matter of immediate concern \Nis next week's mini test.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:10.92,0:17:14.55,Dialogue,Sudo,0,0,0,,But that don't got squat \Nto do with our grades!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.38,0:17:13.86,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps I'll see how \NHorikita does on her own.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:14.55,0:17:16.73,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,If it doesn't influence \Nour academic standing,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:16.73,0:17:18.37,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,then there can be only one reason for it:
Dialogue: 100,0:17:18.75,0:17:22.56,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,The mini test's results will determine \Nthe Paper Shuffle pairings.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.94,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Remember what our teacher said.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:26.67,0:17:32.49,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,The Paper Shuffle sees a pair \Nor two expelled every year.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:33.63,0:17:35.93,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Doesn't that number seem a bit low?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.30,0:17:39.16,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,If all the poorest-performing \Nstudents are grouped together,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:38.01,0:17:40.26,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Are you following this, Sudo?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:39.16,0:17:41.85,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,you'd surely see a dozen or more failures.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:40.26,0:17:42.33,Dialogue,Sudo,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, you bet.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.13,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:44.13,0:17:45.33,Dialogue,Hirata,0,0,0,,Good point!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:45.33,0:17:49.46,Dialogue,Hirata,0,0,0,,You think the pairs are designed \Nto create balanced scores?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.48,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:50.48,0:17:56.09,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,I believe the highest- and lowest-ranking \Nstudents will be paired together
Dialogue: 100,0:17:56.09,0:17:59.59,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,so that all pairs have roughly \Nthe same average score.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.72,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.57,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Which means our goal should be
Dialogue: 100,0:18:03.57,0:18:07.10,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,to precisely pair up those with the \Nhighest and lowest academic performance.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:07.10,0:18:08.97,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,We'll divide all members of Class D
Dialogue: 100,0:18:08.97,0:18:12.12,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,into four blocks based on their \Ncurrent academic standing.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:12.12,0:18:17.61,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Those in the lowest block will \Nleave their test sheets blank.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.08,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:19.08,0:18:22.45,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Then they'll definitely get \Npaired with the highest scorers!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:22.87,0:18:23.79,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:23.79,0:18:27.08,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Similarly, those in the \Nsecond-lowest block
Dialogue: 100,0:18:27.08,0:18:29.75,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,will attempt to get only one question right.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:29.75,0:18:33.75,Dialogue,Hirata,0,0,0,,I see. That'll reduce accidentally \Ndisadvantageous pairings.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:33.75,0:18:36.26,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Are you keeping up with this, Sudo?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:36.26,0:18:37.98,Dialogue,Sudo,0,0,0,,I'm pretty damn clueless.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:37.98,0:18:40.26,Dialogue,Sudo,0,0,0,,Just keeping quiet so I don't get in the way.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:40.26,0:18:42.94,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Hey, you finally get how it works?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:42.94,0:18:45.58,Dialogue,Sudo,0,0,0,,Shaddap! Nobody asked you!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:50.78,0:18:52.81,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,This concludes my proposal.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:53.43,0:18:58.49,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,The remaining question is: which class \Nshould we request to receive our questions?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:58.49,0:19:03.49,Dialogue,Hirata,0,0,0,,Classes A and B are full of students \Nwith high academic performance.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.30,Dialogue,Sudo,0,0,0,,So it sounds like...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:05.30,0:19:08.62,Dialogue,Horikita,0,0,0,,Yes. Class C is our best bet.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:22.89,0:19:26.64,Dialogue,sign,0,0,0,,{\frx20\fry356\fs30\c&H4D4B39&\bord0\shad0\fax-.2\fnTimes New Roman\b1\frz343.4\move(1020,630,918,630)}Call Incoming
Dialogue: 100,0:19:34.41,0:19:37.45,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I told you to limit our contact.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:39.15,0:19:41.03,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:41.03,0:19:44.41,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,I just wanna know what you told Sato-san!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:44.41,0:19:46.30,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}This again?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:46.91,0:19:50.26,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does it matter to you what I told her?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.54,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,It matters a ton!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:52.54,0:19:56.43,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,You threatened me and made \Nme do a bunch of stuff!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:56.43,0:19:59.53,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,So... if Sato-san finds out about that,
Dialogue: 100,0:19:59.53,0:20:02.18,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,it'll lead to some weird rumors about me.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.40,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:03.40,0:20:05.45,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see what you're getting at.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:06.65,0:20:08.85,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,You're worried that if \NI grow close with Sato,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:09.31,0:20:13.07,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,I'll neglect my promise to protect you.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:13.07,0:20:15.06,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is that your first thought?!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.49,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:16.49,0:20:18.87,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not entirely, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:18.87,0:20:21.08,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,I promise, you have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:21.08,0:20:23.28,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you're going out with her?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:24.74,0:20:26.20,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.44,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}You basically did!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:30.37,0:20:32.91,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,I'm getting your true colors \Nloud and clear here.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:32.91,0:20:37.10,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,You think this is your big chance \Nto do some dirty stuff with someone.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.51,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why would you assume that?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:38.94,0:20:41.22,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a tremendous leap in logic.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.51,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:42.51,0:20:45.33,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} leaped right to making \Nme do that weird stuff...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:45.33,0:20:46.72,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:46.94,0:20:49.76,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}If every interaction I have \Nwith a woman is suspect,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:49.76,0:20:51.74,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}what does that mean for Horikita?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:51.74,0:20:54.60,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,I know Horikita-san's not that kind of girl!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:54.60,0:20:58.47,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}She didn't actually ask me out yet, anyway.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:58.47,0:20:59.23,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:59.23,0:21:02.04,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,She said she wanted to keep things platonic,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:02.04,0:21:04.38,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,and requested an exchange \Nof contact information.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:04.81,0:21:07.66,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh... Did she?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:08.02,0:21:10.62,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,So there was nothing to agree to.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:10.62,0:21:15.37,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,But I still bet you hope you \Nget paired up with her, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.55,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Certainly not.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:17.55,0:21:21.35,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Well, I'll let you off the hook for now!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:21.35,0:21:23.51,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}How inexplicably condescending of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:24.59,0:21:25.92,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Not how I meant it!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:25.92,0:21:28.06,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,Anyway, that's all I wanted to know.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:28.06,0:21:28.99,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:28.99,0:21:30.37,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:30.37,0:21:32.43,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to check something.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:32.43,0:21:33.39,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:33.39,0:21:37.27,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Manabe and the others haven't \Ngone after you since then?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:38.21,0:21:40.74,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,No... Not yet.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:41.14,0:21:44.27,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}If anything does happen, tell me right away.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:44.62,0:21:46.33,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter what happens,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:46.65,0:21:48.57,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I swear I'll resolve it.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:54.52,0:21:55.93,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,You'd better.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:55.93,0:21:59.33,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,I mean... that was our agreement and all.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:59.33,0:22:02.17,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}And make sure you delete the record—
Dialogue: 100,0:22:02.17,0:22:05.30,Dialogue,Karuizawa,0,0,0,,...of this call, right? I know.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:05.67,0:22:08.12,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,Perfect. See you later.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:20.71,0:22:25.86,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next day, Horikita explained \Nher plan to the class.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:27.07,0:22:29.77,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}They seemed convinced by her explanation,
Dialogue: 100,0:22:29.77,0:22:32.70,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}and agreed to play along.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:33.51,0:22:37.49,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Swiss zoologist, \NAlfred Portmann, once said
Dialogue: 100,0:22:38.50,0:22:42.00,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}that all humans are born premature.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:43.09,0:22:47.25,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}A newborn human can't even walk on its own.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:47.99,0:22:49.63,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Horikita is the same way.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:49.90,0:22:53.25,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that same underdeveloped nature
Dialogue: 100,0:22:53.25,0:22:55.97,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}is an indication of the capacity \Nfor infinite potential.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:00.83,0:23:05.27,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}An unprecedented sense of unity.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:09.72,0:23:12.20,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's best when I don't have to get involved.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:14.49,0:23:19.27,Dialogue,Chabashira,0,0,0,,I will now announce the \Npairs for Paper Shuffle.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:25.17,0:23:26.67,Dialogue,Sudo,0,0,0,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:34.01,0:23:36.36,Dialogue,Ayanokoji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Incredible, in the worst possible way...
